~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This is INSTALL file for 'Command line parameters parser (CLPP)' library.

Last update: October 28, 2010
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

COMMAND LINE PARAMETERS PARSER
version 2.0.1

Building not required. Just copy 'clpp' folder in a place where your compiler is looking for header files and add:
 
#include <clpp/parser.hpp> 

in your program.
